room_title: Escape room "The Inheritance" by Bangor Escape Rooms in Bangor
room_description: Grandma Ethel was a world traveler who you've just found out has passed away and left you an inheritance. In her will, she described a safe in her office to which you will find it. The other family members have just found out and are furious. They're on their way to find the safe and will be here in an hour. Find it and escape before they show up!
